query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1 acc) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('12.04',
'conic-sections',
'curves',
'dynamical-systems',
'expectation',
'expected-value',
'lie-algebras',
'limits-without-lhopital',
'normed-spaces',
'physics',
'stochastic-calculus',
'updates')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 1
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Analytical',
'Civic Duty',
'Explainer',
'Fanatic',
'Favorite Question',
'Good Answer',
'Great Question',
'Inquisitive',
'Investor',
'Quorum',
'Talkative')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
